 provides the answers you need for everyday solutions.', '20', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=OY9ODwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&source=gbs_api', 'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=OY9ODwAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api', 'un', 1184, 4.1, 435, true, PARSEDATETIME('2018', 'yyyy'), 15, 23, 0);
